      <div n="urn:cts:cdli:P254868.P254868.cdli-en" type="translation" xml:lang="en">
        <l n="1">If a scribe knew/learned (only) one line of text</l>
        <l n="2">And his hand was (nevertheless) very good</l>
        <l n="3">He is a scribe</l>
        <l n="4">If a singer knew/learned (only) one song/hymn</l>
        <l n="5">And his lament/vocalization(?) was (nevertheless) good</l>
        <l n="6">He is a singer/musician</l>
